'From Squeak3.6alpha of ''17 March 2003'' [latest update: #5247] on 18 June 2003 at 11:19:21 am'!"Change Set:		DismissButtonXDate:			18 June 2003Author:			Alexander@Lazarevic.deThis changes the look of the default dismiss button from O to X. This conforms to the use in every other place in the system. Look at a ObjectTool morph to see the change."!!Morph methodsFor: 'menus' stamp: 'laza 6/18/2003 11:06'!dismissButton	"Answer a button whose action would be to dismiss the receiver, and whose action is to send #delete to the receiver"	| aButton |	aButton _ SimpleButtonMorph new.	aButton		target: self topRendererOrSelf;		color:  Color tan;		label: 'X' font: Preferences standardButtonFont;		actionSelector: #delete;		setBalloonText: 'dismiss'.	^ aButton! !